0338726d-14e7-45b1-a9bb-371c0c2b070a.title: Satisfactory
0338726d-14e7-45b1-a9bb-371c0c2b070a.summary: Satisfactory is a first-person open-world factory building game with a dash of exploration and combat. Play alone or with friends, explore an alien planet, create multi-story factories, and enter conveyor belt heaven!

12d61168-f500-4ec9-9627-91bfed04fe87.title: Eve Online
12d61168-f500-4ec9-9627-91bfed04fe87.summary: Eve Online is a space-based, persistent world massively multiplayer online role-playing game developed and published by CCP Games. Players of Eve Online can participate in a number of in-game professions and activities, including mining, piracy, manufacturing, trading, exploration, and combat
